該大學提供兩百多種本科學位及150多種碩士學位，此外還有六十五種研究碩士學位。<ref name="Facts&Figures2012-13">{{cite web|url=http://www.port.ac.uk/media/why-portsmouth/institution/facts-and-figures-2012-2013.pdf|title=Facts & Figures|publisher=''University of Portsmouth''|accessdate=12 August 2013|archive-date=2019-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190629193532/http://www2.port.ac.uk/media/why-portsmouth/institution/facts-and-figures-2012-2013.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>
該大學為私立高等教育機構盎格魯-歐洲[[脊骨神經醫學|脊骨神經醫學]]院（Anglo-European College of Chiropractic）頒發專業碩士學位。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.aecc.ac.uk/cpd-and-postgraduate/postgraduate-programmes/postgraduate-programmes-.aspx | title=Anglo-European College of Chiropractic | accessdate=2 Feb 2011 | archive-date=2011-02-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110202051132/http://www.aecc.ac.uk/cpd-and-postgraduate/postgraduate-programmes/postgraduate-programmes-.aspx | dead-url=no }}</ref>原先也為私立教育機傳統針灸和東方醫學學院（London College of Traditional Acupuncture and Oriental Medicine）頒發針灸榮譽理學士學位和中醫理科碩士學位。但該學院在2011年倒閉。<ref>{{Cite news | url=http://www.timeshighereducation.co.uk/story.asp?sectioncode=26&storycode=414980&c=1 | title=No relief for acupuncture students as private college collapses in debt | date=27 January 2011 | author=Simon Baker | publisher=[[Times_Higher_Education|Times Higher Education]] | accessdate=2013-10-29 | archive-date=2012-01-21 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120121061519/http://www.timeshighereducation.co.uk/story.asp?sectioncode=26&storycode=414980&c=1 | dead-url=no }}</ref>2008年，[[科研評估|科研評估]]將其八個部門評為“世界領先” 在“Allied Health Professions and Studies”、“Applied Mathematics”和“European Studies”的研究質量中排在全英前十。<ref name="Facts&Figures2012-13"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rae.ac.uk/Results/qualityProfile.aspx?id=55&type=hei|title=RAE quality profiles – University of Portsmouth|publisher=''Research Assessment Exercise 2008''|accessdate=12 August 2013|archive-date=2021-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119053850/http://www.rae.ac.uk/Results/qualityProfile.aspx?id=55&type=hei|dead-url=no}}</ref>

